    <item>
      <title>Adnoc 考虑收购价值 50 亿美元的化学品生产商 OCI</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/adnoc-said-to-weigh-takeover-of-5-billion-chemical-producer-oci</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，阿布扎比国家石油公司正在考虑收购欧洲化学品生产商 OCI NV，这是这家中东能源巨头向原油以外业务扩张的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/adnoc-said-to-weigh-takeover-of-5-billion-chemical-producer-oci</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 11:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国委员会质疑德拉克斯利用电力补贴漏洞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/uk-committee-questions-drax-over-use-of-power-subsidy-loophole</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德拉克斯集团在与立法者举行的听证会上为其在能源危机最严重时期利用补贴计划进行了辩护，该计划使其能够赚取巨额利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/uk-committee-questions-drax-over-use-of-power-subsidy-loophole</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 11:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
