    <item>
      <title>香港扩大悬赏金追捕民主活动人士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/hong-kong-expands-use-of-bounties-to-hunt-democracy-activists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港警方悬赏 100 万港元（合 128,000 美元），征集五名居住在海外的当地异见人士的信息，加大力度利用赏金追捕民主活动人士，以维护国家安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/hong-kong-expands-use-of-bounties-to-hunt-democracy-activists</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 10:49:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将购房宽松政策延伸至北京和上海</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/china-extends-homebuying-easing-to-beijing-in-policy-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国当局放松了北京和上海的购房限制，扩大了主要城市遏制前所未有的房地产低迷的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/china-extends-homebuying-easing-to-beijing-in-policy-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 09:27:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威无视全球变化的最后一次加息引发克朗飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/norway-hikes-rate-one-more-time-in-defiance-of-global-mood-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威央行最终推动借贷成本上调，在美联储可能引领全球转向宽松之际，采取行动提振克朗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/norway-hikes-rate-one-more-time-in-defiance-of-global-mood-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 09:09:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士央行呼吁结束加息周期，标志着瑞郎政策的转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/snb-rate-on-hold-as-global-pressure-for-rate-cut-pivot-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士央行宣布结束紧缩周期，并暗示其货币政策将发生转变，在通胀大幅放缓至上限以下后，该行保持借贷成本不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/snb-rate-on-hold-as-global-pressure-for-rate-cut-pivot-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 08:40:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鸽派美联储因宽松押注刺激股票和债券上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储暗示明年降息后，股市和债券上涨，美元走软，在通胀压力缓解的乐观情绪中释放了整个市场的看涨脉搏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
